# Cursor Orchestration Addendum

This document maps the agentic engineering methodology's orchestration concepts to Cursor's Task API.

## Spawning Named Agents

Use the Task tool with `subagent_type` to spawn named agents:

```
Task(subagent_type="engineer", run_in_background=true, prompt="...")
```

Before spawning, read the agent's instruction file at `.cursor/agents/<name>.md` and include the instructions in the Task prompt.

